INSERT INTO `monitors` VALUES ('BDM4350UC','Philips 43\" 4K UHD 60Hz 5ms GTG IPS LED','899.99','See the big picture in vivid detail with the 43\" Ultra HD professional Philips monitor. A 4K UHD resolution produces jaw-dropping image quality while MultiView lets you keep 4 systems open at once so you can multitask like a boss. MHL technology lets you watch mobile content on the big screen.','<ul><li>43-inch display with an UltraClear 4K UHD resolution delivers crystal-clear imagery and life-like picture quality </li><li>5ms response helps reduce motion blur to make fast-action scenes appear smooth</li><li>SmartConnect with DisplayPort, HDMI, and VGA inputs allow for seamless connectivity </li><li>MHL technology lets you enjoy mobile content on the big screen</li><li>USB 3.0 hub lets you access content from a USB flash drive and offers fast charging</li><li>IPS LED wide view technology produces natural colours for an immersive viewing experience from any angle</li><li>MultiView lets you have 4 systems on one screen, all in beautiful 4K</li><li>SmartUniformity mode delivers accurate images in terms of brightness, delivering consistency for all your photography, design, and printing</li><li>Configure image settings easily with the SmartImage presets </li><li>Powerful 7-watt speakers provide superior sound</li><li>Slim bezel design offers a stylish look</li><li>VESA mount allows you to configure the perfect setup </li><li>ENERGY STAR qualified to help keep your utility bills down </li></ul>'),('GF276ABMIPX','Acer 27\" 1080p HD 75Hz TN LED','279.99','In competitive gaming, every frame matters. The Acer GF276 gaming monitor features Full HD 1080p resolution and AMD FreeSync technology, giving you a serious competitive edge. With VGA, DVI, and HDMI connectivity, you can display images from a PC, laptop, or even your smartphone. With a sleek zero-frame design, it\'s ideal for multiple monitor setups.','<ul><li>27-inch LED backlit display with Full HD 1920 x 1080 resolution delivers excellent detail, making it perfect for your favourite multimedia content, Full HD gaming, and productivity tasks</li><li>Acer Zero Frame space-saving design with X-shaped stand fits in a variety of spaces and allows you to place multiple monitors (each sold separately) side by side to create a seamless digital workspace</li><li>1ms response time delivers ultra-smooth action and improved in-game response time</li><li>AMD FreeSync technology with 75Hz refresh rate delivers a tear-free experience</li><li>ASUS Eye Care technology with Flicker-free and Ultra-Low Blue Light minimizes eye fatigue over those prolonged gaming sessions</li><li>100 million:1 contrast ratio produces pure whites and deep blacks</li><li>Connectivity options include VGA and HDMI, allowing you to enjoy Full HD display on your smartphone or tablet</li></ul>'),('LC49HG90DMNXZA','Samsung 49\" Ultrawide 144Hz 1ms Curved LED','1499.99','When it comes to smoother gameplay and seamless multitasking, the Samsung CHG90 QLED gaming monitor sets the bar high. Its 49\" ultra-wide 32:9 curved screen immerses your field of view, and modes like Easy Setting Box and PBP make true multitasking possible. Quantum dot technology and HDR support ensure breathtaking colour and contrast.','<ul><li>49\" curved monitor with 3840 x 1080 WQHD resolution displays content with mesmerizing detail to immerse you in your gaming marathons, movies, and more</li><li>Ultra-wide 32:9 aspect ratio is equivalent to two 27-inch 16:9 monitors side-by-side to make true multitasking with a single monitor possible</li><li>1800R curved screen draws you into the action, so you\'ll be fully immersed in any game you\'re playing</li><li>1ms response time and 144hz refresh rate combine with Samsung\'s advanced motion blur reduction technology to make fast-paced action scenes and gaming sequences appear smooth as butter</li><li>Enjoy the option of choosing 60Hz, 120Hz, or 144Hz refresh rate based on your game and hardware specs</li><li>Metal Quantum dot technology produces colour in a way that’s incredibly fine and dense so everything on-screen looks impeccably sharp, vibrant, and lifelike</li><li>QLED supports High Dynamic Range (HDR) for images with a wider range of luminance levels that render dark areas deeper and light areas brighter</li><li>AMD FreeSync 2 technology defines a higher bar for smooth HDR gaming and delivers exceptional brightness and colour volume</li><li>Advanced VA panel minimizes light leakage across the screen and corners and produces a 3,000:1 contrast ratio, so you see rich blacks and bright whites in any scene</li><li>Multiple game display modes instantly optimize black gamma levels, contrast ratios, sharpness, and colour value settings for any game genre</li><li>20-step Black Equalizer technology adjusts any game scene to the brightness level you want, letting you spot enemies hiding in even the darkest areas of the screen</li><li>Audio-synced Arena Lighting amps up your gaming experience with a pulsing lightshow</li><li>One DisplayPort, one Mini DisplayPort, two HDMI ports, and one headphone output offer versatility for connecting other displays, headphones, and more</li><li>Easy Setting Box technology lets you partition the screen or display multiple screens of different sizes with just a click</li><li>Picture-by-Picture (PBP) mode allows you to view 2 different input sources on the screen while maintaining the picture quality of the source</li><li>Eye Saver mode and Flicker Free technology cut down on blue light emissions and help fight eye fatigue, so you can work and play longer without strained eyes</li><li>OSD dashboard menu blends in with game interfaces, making it look like it\'s all part of the game</li><li>The Height Adjustable Stand (HAS) provides precise positioning for the super ultra-wide panel to make long hours at work or play as comfortable as possible </li></ul>'),('LU28H750UQNXZA','Samsung 28\" 4K UHD 60Hz 1ms TN LED Qdot','549.99','Enjoy fine detail, vivid colour, and a wider workspace with this Samsung 28\" 4K UHD monitor. Its stellar 3840 x 2160 resolution and quantum dot technology complement each other beautifully so that every crisp image practically pops off the screen. Meanwhile, the PIP and PBP screen function empowers the multitasker in us all.','<ul><li>28\" Quantum Dot display boasts 4K Ultra HD resolution showcasing an impressive 8 million pixels on screen -- that\'s 4x greater than Full HD</li><li>1ms response time eliminates motion blur, judder, and ghosting to make fast-paced action scenes and gaming sequences appear smooth as butter</li><li>AMD FreeSync dynamically syncs the screen refresh rate with the image frame rate to optimize gameplay with minimal stutter</li><li>Quantum Dot technology blends an endless amount of quantum dots with 1 billion hues so that every colour on screen is vividly and vibrantly displayed </li><li>sRGB 125% helps deliver a wider spectrum of accurate colours that stay sharp even in bright lighting conditions</li><li>Game Mode instantly optimizes screen contrast and colours so that you see gaming scenes at their best</li><li>Picture-in-Picture (PIP) lets you resize the second image to cover up to 25% of the screen and position it anywhere</li><li>Picture-by-Picture (PBP) dual screen function lets you connect to 2 different devices at the same time while still maintaining the original image quality</li><li>2 HDMI ports, 1 DisplayPort input, and 1 headphone output offer versatility for connecting other displays, headphones, and more</li><li>Eye Saver mode and Flicker Free technology cut down on blue light emissions and help fight eye fatigue, so you can work and play longer without strained eyes</li><li>The thin profile, narrow bezel, and slender metallic Y stand of this monitor make it a discreet, modern accent to your home or office decor</li></ul>'),('MX27UC','Asus 27\" 4K UHD 60 Hz 5 ms GTG LED','799.99','ASUS Designo MX27UC feels right at home in any living space, with a space-saving ultra-slim profile that measures just 1.25cm at its thinnest point. Like its contemporaries in the Designo MX family, Designo MX27UC features an exquisite edge-to-edge frameless panel with a bezel measuring just 0.1cm thick.','<p>Exquisite ultra-slim, frameless design</p>'),('PA329Q','ASUS PA329Q 32\" 4K/UHD HDMI Eye Care ProArt','1720.99','The PA329Q is the requisite monitor for content professionals, featuring 4K UHD resolution with 99.5-Percent Adobe RGB for color-critical projects where precision matters.','<p>• 32-Inch 4K UHD (3840 x 2160) resolution display with DisplayPort 1.2, mini-DisplayPort 1.2 and 4x HDMI 2.0 inputs</p><p>• 100-Percent Rec.709 and 99.5-Percent Adobe RGB true color reproduction, factory precalibrated for outstanding color accuracy (DeltaE and lt;2). Supports DIC-P3 and Rec. 2020 color standards</p><p>• ASUS ProArt Calibration technology with 14-bit look-up table (LUT) and uniformity compensation capability</p><p>• Compatible with major hardware calibrators such as X-rite i1 Display Pro and Datacolor Spyder 5 series, with ability to save color parameter profiles directly to the monitor (accessible via hotkey)</p><p>• Ergonomic tilt, swivel, pivot and height adjustment stand with ASUS Eye Care flicker-free and low blue light technologies</p>'),('PD3200U','BenQ 32\" 4K UHD 60Hz 4ms GTG S-IPS LED','899.99','The BENQ PD3200U 32\" 4K Designer monitor is ideal for graphic designers, video editors, and a host of other creative professionals. It features 100% sRGB and Rec. 709 color space to accurately reproduce over 1 billion colours on screen. It has a 3840 x 2160 UHD resolution and multiple picture modes that help you get meticulous with post-production work.','<ul><li>32\" LED edge-lit display with 3840 x 2160 UHD resolution presents all multimedia with immaculate clarity and sharpness</li><li>Perfect for photographers, graphic designers, producers, video editors, and other creative professionals</li><li>IPS technology provides 178-degree wide viewing angles, giving you the ability to work with vivid clarity from multiple angles</li><li>100% sRGB and Rec. 709 color space accurately reproduce more than 1 billion vibrant colours on screen</li><li>CAD/CAM Mode offers exceptional contrast of technical illustrations to bring out the smallest details</li><li>Animation Mode lets you lighten images to help you see hidden details</li><li>DualView lets you view designs in 2 picture modes side-by-side for enhanced efficiency and productivity</li><li>Darkroom mode adjusts brightness and contrast, creating optimal settings for designers working in darkened post-production environments</li><li>Hotkey Puck is a customizable button that makes it easy to toggle between picture modes</li><li>KVM Switch function allows users to display and control the contents from two different PC systems using just one screen, keyboard, and mouse</li><li>Connectivity options include a DisplayPort input, HDMI, and four USB 3.0 ports</li><li>Flicker-Free and Low Blue Light technology work together to reduce eye strain and fatigue over those long working hours</li><li>Features height, tilt, pivot, stroke, and swivel monitor adjustments, and even auto-adjusts when positioned in a vertical orientation</li></ul>'),('PG348Q','Asus 34\" ROG Ultrawide WQHD 5ms GTG Curved LED','1349.99','Get the drop on your competition with the ASUS 34\" ROG Swift curved gaming monitor. Precision crafted to give you the ultimate competitive edge, it features an eye-popping 3440 x 1440 QHD resolution, easy-access hot keys to unlock a range of gamer-specific on-screen weapons, and visual settings that minimize eyestrain over marathon gaming sessions.','<ul><li>Ultra-wide 34-inch IPS display with a bewitching QHD resolution of 3440 x 1440 and a 21:9 aspect ratio gives you tons of screen real estate to immerse yourself in mesmerizing game worlds </li><li>NVIDIA G-Sync technology allows you to overclock the refresh rate to 100Hz refresh rate, eliminating lag and killing motion blur (requires a GeForce GTX 980Ti or above; not included) </li><li>Curved panel design means your eyes are always an equal distance from all points on the monitor, pulling you further and further into the action on screen </li><li>100% sRGB colour gamut and 1000:1 contrast ratio delivers tantalizing, lifelike colours and deep, rich blacks to bring fantastic digital worlds to vivid life </li><li>Built-in Turbo Keys on the back of the panel let you trigger different refresh rates instantly, without having to dig into cumbersome graphic control settings </li><li>ASUS EyeCare technology lowers blue light settings and screen flickering to minimize eyestrain, so there\'s no drop-off in your alertness or skill level during those marathon gaming sessions </li><li>5-way on-screen joystick makes it easy to navigate system settings and select between different visual features </li><li>GamePlus hot keys let you add a steady crosshair, multi-purpose timer, or informative FPS (frames per second) counter as graphic overlays, giving you an extra edge over your otherwise in-the-dark opponents </li><li>GameVisual pre-sets optimize the visual settings of the display for specific game types, so you can jump from a shooter to an MMORPG without </li></ul>'),('S2817Q','Dell 28\" 4K UHD 60Hz 2ms GTG TN LED','649.99','Elevate your entertainment with this Dell 28\" monitor. It displays 4K UHD resolution for lifelike detail and vibrant colours. A 2ms response time and 60Hz refresh rate delivers smooth action without ghosting or lag. Multiple connectivity options let you see content from 2 different sources with Picture-in-Picture and Picture-by-Picture features.','<ul><li>28-inch LED back-lit LCD display with 4K UHD (3840 x 2160) resolution delivers true-to-life images for an exceptional viewing experience, ideal for gamers and demanding professionals who do detailed work like editing photos and videos</li><li>2ms panel response time with a 60Hz refresh rate lets you enjoy fluid, accurate movement during rapid action sequences without ghosting and lag</li><li>Connectivity options include: 1 DisplayPort, 1 mini DisplayPort, 2 HDMI input, 2 USB 3.0 ports, and 1 audio line-out</li><li>Multiple ports let you multi-task and view content from 2 different sources using Picture-in-Picture and Picture-by-Picture display options</li><li>Thin bezel design offers near edge-to-edge viewing for immersive gameplay or viewing</li><li>Built-in dual 9W speakers offer a full home theatre-style experience adding rich sound to your stunning visuals</li><li>ENERGY STAR certified keeps energy consumption low, which is great for your wallet and the planet</li></ul>'),('XG27VQ','ASUS ROG Strix 27\" FHD 144Hz 4ms Curved LED','499.99','Game on. The ASUS 27\" ROG Strix gaming monitor features a 144Hz refresh rate and Adaptive Sync/FreeSync paired with 1800R curvature for smooth, immersive gaming experiences. Swivel, tilt, and height adjustability let you easily find your ideal viewing position. Game for hours on end with less eyestrain thanks to ASUS Eye Care technology.','<ul><li>Full HD resolution offers crisper, more immense detail and more valuable desktop space</li><li>Curved monitor design means your eyes are always an equal distance from all points on the monitor, pulling you further and further into the action on screen</li><li>144Hz refresh rate and 4ms response time minimizes lag and motion blur, so you\'ll experience smooth visuals in the fastest action sequences</li><li>Adaptive Sync/FreeSync offers for immersive, smooth gaming with DisplayPort, HDMI, and DVI connectivity</li><li>ASUS Eye Care technology features a blue light filter and flicker-free backlighting to cut down on eyestrain during epic gaming sessions</li><li>Tilt, pivot, swivel, and height adjustments help you find a game-grade, ergonomic position for your gaming and entertainment needs</li><li>GamePlus and GameVisual now supports MOBA mode with colour enhancements for more focused gameplay</li><li>ASUS Aura RGB lighting on the back and LED lighting projection in the base lets you customize the look </li></ul>');
